{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "经历了“黑色魔兽”一劫\\n而幸免于难的村民们\\n开始跟随丽雅学习战斗技巧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "他们中的一部分人逐渐成长为\\n能与魔兽战斗的存在，\\n并以丽雅为中心组成了魔兽讨伐部队。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "你冲得太靠前了！\\n要先把敌人引诱出来再进行攻击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "部下1",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "侧面也有魔兽过来了，\\n谁能去阻挡？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "部下2",
            "context": "交给我吧！呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "不错！就这样压制住！\\n哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "呼……歼灭完毕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "部下1",
            "context": "我们成功了呢！丽雅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "大家干得不错。\\n不过也有很多地方值得反思。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "回去之后要针对你们的不足\\n进行特训，做好心理准备了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01",
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "部下们",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01",
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "丽雅的部队活跃在大陆各地，\\n许多人因憧憬他们而造访圣城。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120055_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族1",
            "context": "丽雅从魔兽手中救下了我们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族2",
            "context": "而且我们从她战斗的英姿中\\n得到了勇气。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族2",
            "context": "我们不想再过每天\\n害怕魔兽来袭的日子了。所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120055_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族1",
            "context": "我们会用弓，\\n虽然没有与魔兽战斗的经验……\\n但我们还是想和她并肩作战！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好的，我去问问丽雅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120055_01",
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族们",
            "context": "谢谢你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "丽雅的部队可真受欢迎啊，\\n这已经是第几个人了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且聚过来的人\\n也不分种族不分高低贵贱。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "丽雅的部队越是活跃，\\n像这样想要与魔兽战斗\\n而前来的人们一定会越多吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那样的话，还是重新组织一下\\n组建更大规模的部队比较好吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊，既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "你说要组建骑士团？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，我们打算在这座城里\\n组建讨伐魔兽的骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不分高低贵贱、自由的骑士团。\\n当然，圣城会负责相关支援。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "而骑士团的团长，\\n就是你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "诶？我来当团长！？\\n这个……虽说我很乐意，\\n可我能胜任这个职位吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "会因愤怒而失去理智的我，\\n怎么当得了团长……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "说什么呢，你现在不也出色地\\n指挥着那个村子的人们吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "况且正因为是你，才能指引\\n聚来的有志之士不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "正因为是我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那些想要与你并肩作战的人们\\n多多少少都因为魔兽\\n而留下了痛苦的回忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以一定会有怀着恨意战斗的人吧。\\n也许会像过去的丽雅那样失去理智。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而你能为他们指引方向，\\n不让他们犯下过错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且很多人都在你的影响下\\n萌发了与魔兽战斗的意志。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就像你父亲曾为村民们带去勇气一样，\\n引导这份意志的责任，\\n只有你才能够肩负啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "在我的影响下萌发了\\n与魔兽战斗的意志……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "是啊……正确引导他们的意志，\\n正是我的责任呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n我愿意担任骑士团团长。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢你，丽雅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那就赶快召集有志之士，\\n举行骑士团成立仪式吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我来当你们的见证人，\\n丽雅发表一下团长就任演说吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "在众人面前发表演说……唔……\\n我该说些什么，又该怎么说呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "讲讲你打算让这个骑士团\\n发展成什么样不就好了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "要是想不出什么好的演说词，\\n借用别人的话也可以哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "理想中的骑士团……别人的话……\\n那就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "圣城中庭——\\n在尤蒂尔的见证下，\\n举行了骑士团成立仪式。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "丽雅环视了有志之士的面容，\\n庄严而有力地发表宣言。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "我所尊敬的一位骑士曾说过，\\n“骑士之剑当为人，\\n己之愿当藏于心。”",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "当时年幼的我，\\n没能理解这句话的含义。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "但自从来到这座城，受到众人的帮助，\\n我终于理解了这句话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "剑是为守护他人而挥动的武器，\\n而被守护的人，\\n也终将成为守护他人的剑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "这个骑士团的战斗，\\n将成为尚未得到守护之人的曙光。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "正因如此，我们不希望任何人\\n怀着憎恨或悲伤去战斗。\\n贯彻正义的信念与骄傲才是我们的初衷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "我愿引领这骑士团成为每个人\\n都怀抱荣誉而战的骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "没错——成为每个人的头上\\n都闪耀着荣光的骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01",
                "120019_01",
                "120056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "有志之士们",
            "context": "丽雅团长，万岁！\\n圣城骑士团，万岁！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "丽雅，我很期待你的骑士团\\n今后的活跃和发展。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "嗯，为了不辜负你的这份期待，\\n我会竭尽全力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "这把剑，与高洁的骑士同在——\\n我一定会让他所留下的\\n勇气之蕾开花结果。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110259_01_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}